h1_title: How to Find the Five Skandhas and Unlock a Secret Boss
h2_title: How to Find the Skandha of Choice
content: When you get to the end, you'll see a pathway leading up to the right and white sacs to the left of it. Behind these sacs is a bridge that will take you down to where you want to go.
